jspecview.util
Class JDXSourceStringTokenizer

java.lang.Object
  jspecview.util.JDXSourceStringTokenizer

public class JDXSourceStringTokenizer
extends java.lang.Object

JDXSourceStringTokenizer breaks up the JDXSource into pairs of Label Data Records (LDRs). When nextToken() is called, the label and value variables are updated.

Author:
Debbie-Ann Facey, Khari A. Bryan, Prof Robert J. Lancashire
See Also:
